<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-9931] camel-kafka - Add support for async sending with callback</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-9931</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This requires us having a thread pool on the component that is used for processing the async replies when the kafka callback signals. Because we should not use its thread to continue routing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
